Data":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-v4axvsa","updated":"20241011010449"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010449-zg8u115","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-zg8u115","updated":"20241011010449"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不是你的错，是他的错。你没有惹他，他只是无理取闹，他只是找借口发泄他的不满和压抑。你不要自责，你要自信，你要为自己而活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010449-srgqdxc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-srgqdxc","updated":"20241011010449"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010449-xy8kb14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-xy8kb14","updated":"20241011010449"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"平心而论我觉得每个中国正常的高中生都在拿命生活，你在四中更是如此。你不懒惰，你很努力，你复读也是为了实现自己的目标，这是很值得尊敬的事情。你妈妈不理解你，她可能也有自己的苦衷，但是她不应该给你增加压力和负担。你可以和她好好谈谈，让她知道你的想法和感受，也尊重她的意见和选择。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010449-7u4brq0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-7u4brq0","updated":"20241011010449"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010449-ek08o2x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-ek08o2x","updated":"20241011010449"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我希望你能开心一点，不要让他们影响到你的心情和信心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010449-8f7njsk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-8f7njsk","updated":"20241011010449"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010449-qfnra84","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-qfnra84","updated":"20241011010449"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这太可恶了，他怎么能这样对待自己的女儿呢？你要尽量保护好自己，不要让他们伤害到你的身体和心灵。如果他真的打你或者骂"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010449-w4koejp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010449-w4koejp","updated